  "difficulty": null,
  "summary": "鸽巢原理简单应用题，发现对于前 8 个数，选或不选最后得出的状态数为 $255 > 200$，说明无论如何<strong>只用 8 个数就能出现重复</strong>的下标取法了，所以本题直接暴力求子集即可。",
  "link": "https://atcoder.jp/contests/abc200/tasks/abc200_d",
  "link_text": "D - Happy Birthday! 2",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": null,
  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定一个由 $N$ 个正整数组成的数列 $A = (A_1, A_2, \\dots, A_N)$。请判断是否存在满足以下所有条件的两个数列 $B = (B_1, B_2, \\dots, B_x)$ 和 $C = (C_1, C_2, \\dots, C_y)$，如果存在，请输出其中一组。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$1 \\leq x, y \\leq N$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$1 \\leq B_1 < B_2 < \\dots < B_x \\leq N$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$1 \\leq C_1 < C_2 < \\dots < C_y \\leq N$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$B$ 和 $C$ 是不同的数列。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "当 $x \\neq y$ 时，或者存在某个整数 $i\\ (1 \\leq i \\leq \\min(x, y))$ 使得 $B_i \\neq C_i$ 时，$B$ 和 $C$ 被认为是不同的。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$A_{B_1} + A_{B_2} + \\dots + A_{B_x}$ 除以 $200$ 的余数与 $A_{C_1} + A_{C_2} + \\dots + A_{C_y}$ 除以 $200$ 的余数相等。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "输入以以下格式从标准输入读入。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "> $N$ $A_1$ $A_2$ $\\dots$ $A_N$",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$2 \\leq N \\leq 200$",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$1 \\leq A_i \\leq 10^9$",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果不存在满足条件的数列组 $B, C$，请输出一行 <code>No</code>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果存在，请按以下格式输出 $B, C$：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "> Yes $x$ $B_1$ $B_2$ $\\dots$ $B_x$ $y$ $C_1$ $C_2$ $\\dots$ $C_y$",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
